title: BRIEF-Talex gets orders from Eurocash
text:
BRIEF-Talex gets orders from Eurocash 
Oct 12 Talex SA : 
* Since Nov. 4, 2014 got orders from Eurocash SA for delivery of IT services for total value of 5.56 million zlotys ($1.50 million) net Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: ($1 = 3.7089 zlotys) (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
